{"tid":258341,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【海之戀無限touch】無殼羅仲謙：我係首置客 想買一個單位做投資！","createTime":"2017-05-26T04:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T00:03:38.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56baad9818db70ec7f59629bbeb3068d259417a9","tid":258341,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170526/large/1495770860_8d13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170526%2Flarge%2F1495770860_8d13.jpg&h=7ca39891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人羅仲謙今日現身荃灣海之戀售樓處，他表示，自己沒有物業，屬首置人士，想買一個兩房以上單位作投資用途，已入票抽籤，又指自己抽籤買樓欠運氣，上次抽將軍澳緻藍天都抽不到，今次睇咁多人爭，場面咁熱鬧，相信買到都的機會亦不大，如買不到心水便等下一次。對於點睇樓市，他稱自己不懂樓市，最重要是衡量自己負擔能力，但認為投資磚頭較為穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n記者要求佢不如除低口罩影張相，他很有禮貌地說因和朋友一齊不方便。"},{"pid":"a57978f65c149e4684dae484af8636a5026f92aa","tid":258341,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170526/56744655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170526%2F56744655&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d891126c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170526%2F56744655&h=90082cb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170526/56744655</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389950ee7cf85d322907d6c54c66b3db56e569d6","tid":258341,"uid":46910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"炒樓死全家"},{"pid":"85050d3256219ae5063f7ef9c75736e7948ef437","tid":258341,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:03:38.000Z","msg":"係咪要每飲一啖都除口罩"}]}